<h4 id="definition">Definition</h4>
<p>One of the most important subgroups of $S_n$ is the set of all even
permutations, $A_n$. The group $A_n$ is called the $\textbf{alternating group on}$ 
n $\textbf{letters}$.</p>

<h4 id="theorem">Theorem</h4>
<ol>
  <li>The set $A_n$ is a subgroup of $S_n$</li>
</ol>

